data.description: This pristine 2021-built home is nestled on a corner lot, with no neighbors directly behind.  This property features three bedrooms alongside a flexible den, offering endless possibilities for your lifestyle. The heart of the home, a sleek kitchen, effortlessly flows into the open-concept living and dining areas, creating a warm and inviting space for daily living and entertaining. The master suite, a sanctuary of its own, boasts a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom. Outside, a charming backyard with a patio provides the perfect backdrop for outdoor gatherings or moments of relaxation.
